communities.name: Briar Chapel
communities.description:
Make yourself at home at Porto Bello Estates, a community of single family homes in St. Mary’s County, MD. Located just minutes away from Rt. 2/4, homeowners at Porto Bello Estates will enjoy the convenience and luxury that come with this premiere location.

These beautiful, wooded 1+ acre lots provide enough space for a pool in the backyard or a 3- car garage. You can entertain your family and friends with pool parties and cookouts or just relax and enjoy the tranquil surroundings.

Visit the community: From Patuxent Beach Road, turn Left onto Three Notch Rd. Right onto MD-237 S/Chancellors Run Rd. Right onto Great Mills Rd. Left onto Point Lookout Rd. Left on Flat Iron Rd. Continue on Drayden Rd. Continue on Frogs Marsh Rd. Go past the existing community and follow the signs to the new section.

communities.name: Georges Grant

With a convenient location at the intersection of Norwood and Six Forks Road, these 14 home sites will not last long.

Choose from our portfolio of plans or bring your own and we can customize and personalize your new home for the way you want to live.  

Come visit our model home today!

communities.name: Hamptons at Umstead
communities.description:
The Hamptons is located on Ebenezer Church Road in NW Raleigh and offers 215 beautiful wooded large acreage home sites.

These custom homes enhance the neighborhoods picturesque views. It boasts a planned multilevel clubhouse with fitness room, lap pool and children's play areas and direct access to the Raleigh greenway system at neighboring Umstead State Park.  

Come visit our model home today!

communities.name: Heritage
communities.description:
Amenities include the Heritage Golf Club, a semi-private course with a 4.5 Star rating, the Heritage Swim and Tennis Club with two swimming pools, lazy river, club house and playgrounds. Miles of walking and biking trails throughout the Wake Forest Greenway, fishing pond, soccer fields, parks, picnic pavilions and playgrounds are just a few of the ways you can spend your time in Heritage.  

Restaurants, grocery stores, pharmacies, and more are all right within the community and just a minutes drive! The factory which is a giant sports complex is right within in the community as well offering ice skating, basketball, soccer, ballet, dance, karate, crafts and more!

communities.name: Stonehenge Park
communities.description:
Stonehenge Park is located near Stonehenge Shopping Center, Brier Creek, North Hills, restaurants, shopping, and Raleigh-Durham Airport! It offers upscale charm, distinctive elevations and all the features of our high-performance green homes.

Choose from ranch, first floor master, and classic two story plans that fit your needs and lifestyle.

Come visit our model home today!
